emporally-stable structures for roosting during the summer maternity season.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Lacki, Michael J.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/edcc1e123e73c05b221fdd895311044f", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/6de2b2cffce788ddd105433497402bf1055d801d5aa5070364911e19f7385581", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/EWKWKISF", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/EWKWKISF", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/8fb5d7dc93006b04426bba75d84cad82!/b61872-64406", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "2", "pages": "29", "title": "Diversity", "volume": "10"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/edcc1e123e73c05b221fdd895311044f"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:EWKWKISF"}, {"identifier": "10.3390/d10020029"}], "communities": [{"id": "batlit"}, {"id": "biosyslit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "13452297"}}]}}, "title": "Restoration of Legacy Trees as Roosting Habitat for Myotis Bats in Eastern North American Forests", "links": {"self": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/13452298", "self_html": "https://zenodo.